(270, 'E', 2, 'Efficiency isn''t about how many lines you wrote, but how much trouble you solved with the lines you kept.', 'Essence of efficiency', 'en'),
(271, 'E', 2, 'Real efficiency is lowering the cognitive load of the entire system. If others can read your intent instantly, you’ve won.', 'Long-term value', 'en'),
