(343, 'F', 2, 'Listen to the "silence" of the code. When it won’t run, that error message is your only high-dimensional dialogue with the underlying system.', 'Deep feedback view', 'en'),
(344, 'E', 0, 'Manually formatting code is an assault on your fingers. Leave the heavy lifting to Prettier and save your brain for the logic.', 'Automation correction', 'en'),
(345, 'E', 1, 'Stop obsessing over micro-optimizations unless they actually hinder the user. Make it work, then make it fast.', 'Premature optimization warning', 'en'),
(346, 'E', 2, 'Behind every O(1) complexity lies O(n) thinking. Before you write the first line, think about your compute allocation.', 'Depth of thought', 'en'),
(347, 'F', 0, 'Stop feeding AI your emotional venting. It’s a silicon-based lifeform; it can’t feel your anxiety, only your tokens.', 'Objective communication', 'en'),
(348, 'F', 1, 'Every successful prompt interaction is a high-speed "thought sync." Make sure you’re both on the same channel.', 'Synchronized thinking', 'en'),
(349, 'F', 2, 'Learn to appreciate the "unexpected" solutions AI offers. It’s not a bug; it’s a fragment of inspiration fished from a sea of training data.', 'Inspiration capture', 'en'),
